     Facebook further provided the Upload IP address of the child pornography as 73.250.110.160.  An open source check of the IP address showed the IP address came back to Comcast with a geo-location of Elkton, Maryland.  Cpl Heid viewed the 2 videos which both depict child pornography.  The descriptions are as follows:

1. Filename: YWNatrNQSBMcl8lA355841041_7141459332537803_3629633862362391216_n.mp4.  This two minute and twenty-second video depicts what appears to be an adult black male sodomizing a black male child before ejaculating in the child's anus.  The child is seen bent over from behind but does not appear to be fully developed.
2. Filename:  TqMHjPBmWq53xce8373438661_6539214289477966_6776583736602411645_n.mp4.  This is a one minute and fifth one-second video depicts a young white/hispanic female reasonably believed to be 8-10 years of age.  The child is nude on her back while being vaginally penetrated by what appears to be an adult male.

     Cpl. Heid sent a subpoena request to Comcast for the listed IP address through the Howard County State's Attorney's Office.  Cpl. Heid will be awaiting it's return before any additional investigation.  The case remains open at this time.
